    <section class="information">
        <title>Short description</title>
        <p>Santorini is a volcanic island in the Cyclades group of the Greek islands. It is famous
            for dramatic views, stunning sunsets from <a href="#poi.oia">Oia town</a>, the strange
            white aubergine (eggplant), the town of Thira and naturally its very own active <a href="#poi.volcano">volcano</a>. There are naturally fantastic beaches such as the
            black sand beach of <a href="#poi.perissa">Perissa</a>, maybe the best beach in
            Santorini.</p>
    </section>
