                <data>
                    <row>
                    <description facilities="Restaurant">
                        <p>The nearly barren island <place>Nea Kameni</place> is visited daily by
                            dozens of tourist boats throughout the summer. Visitors climb a gravel
                            path to reach the top of the 130-meter-high volcanic crater, where it is
                            possible to complete a full circuit of the rim. </p>
